### Objective 6 — Define Product Scope with Precision

**In Scope:**
- Sovereign enterprise communication
- Zero-Knowledge infrastructure design
- Offline resilience through Survival Mesh
- Federated cross-organization collaboration
- Hardware-backed cryptographic identity
- AI integration with privacy preservation
- Extension ecosystem with WASM sandbox isolation

**Out of Scope:**
- Plaintext storage on any server
- Cloud-provider-dependent architecture
- Server-side content inspection or metadata analysis
- Remote code execution outside sandboxed `.tapp` environments
- Consumer social messaging use cases

